enhanced_by.reason: Both methods involve generating or retrieving a key based on the field's properties.
The getKey method relies on the indexed status of the field, which is determined by the isIndexed method.
The getKey method returns a key derived from the field's property, similar to how getProperty returns the property itself.
The getKey method may include the indexed list property in its key generation, similar to how getIndexedListProperty returns the indexed list property.
